summary: uh so i um made an uh......moomin oc..... his name is Soot, he lives in his little house boat(that i might still be designing??)...
caption:
uh so i um made an uh……moomin oc…..

his name is Soot, he lives in his little house boat(that i might still be designing??) and ended up ship wrecked in moomin valley. ship wrecked as in the wind drifted him off into the shallows and now he’s just kinda stuck? which is fine, he’s got his bakery and a lot of the locals seem to like his treats and goods. although he does miss travelling the seas…he is very happy he found moomin valley becos he’s honestly really lonely. he does enjoy his alone time, seeing as he’s pretty introverted and anxious(which is why he wears the hood), but he really loves to make friends and be around others.

Soot is very cold sensitive and before ending up near the moomins, he would chase hot weather to stay comfortable and toasty. When it gets cold, he tends to just go right to sleep which he finds to be a bit of a waste of time. He likes to keep himself busy, baking and running around, but when its warm out he tends to just relax in the sun, usually lounging on nice hot rocks. kinda like a reptile i guess?

i also would like to add that when he does sleep for the winter, it’s usually upside down, hanging by his tail. any other day he just burrows into a pile of blankets. but, seeing as heat rises, hanging from the rafters works best for him.
